GOAL: Analyze GitHub repositories to identify language popularity, repository trends, topic adoption, and repository activity patterns.

DATA SOURCE: GitHub REST API

LAYERS:
    Bronze: Raw GitHub JSON responses
    Silver: Cleaned repository and topic tables
    Gold: Aggregated analytics tables

DASHBOARD METRICS:
    1. Most popular languages
    2. Repository count by language
    3. Language growth over time
    4. Top repositories by stars
    5. Top repositories by forks
    6. Repository creation trend
    7. Stars distribution
    8. Repository activity
    9. Repository age vs popularity
    10. Most popular topics
    11. Topic growth
    12. Stars by topic
